{"tid":2316523,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"柒婆同許勇，邊個可信啲？","createTime":"2020-12-08T03:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T03:02:21.000Z","uid":3513,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e60293a43e06928b87c854377ac600aab94ceeb0","tid":2316523,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:01:22.000Z","msg":"#許智峯流亡 <br />\n林鄭月娥斥許向法庭說謊、無公信力<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2LdpQBT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LdpQBT&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=0f371592\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2LdpQBT</a><br />\n<br />\n前立法會議員許智峯及其家人的戶口被凍結，今早舉行行政會議前，林鄭月娥被問到會否影響香港國際金融中心地位及信譽，她指事件是有人向法庭說謊，以在保釋期間離開香港，又稱「政府同一個難以可以有公信力嘅人比較呢，就係政府做嘢係有規有矩」，政府「要講證據」，亦不能透露調查內容。她再次指責網上及社交媒體的「假資訊」抹黑其他機構及人士，呼籲「某一個人講嘅說話有無份量，你又會唔會信，你都要諗下呢個人有咩前科。呢個特別嘅人士有咩前科，我唔需要喺度再重覆喇。」<br />\n<br />\n《有線新聞》記者問及警方連日拘捕多名民主派人士，林鄭月娥稱不便評論，但指香港要「撥亂反正」，需重新建立法治社會，「有法必依，犯法就係犯法」，不能因為犯法是民主派人士「就唔做嘢」，有「護身罩」，又稱香港「並無法外之地。」<br />\n<br />\nSource: 獨媒"},{"pid":"b55cc3d04757c8810cfb598a491ed927410fea1a","tid":2316523,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:01:47.000Z","msg":"柒婆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n許勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c087abb4c07822163e9980f0d597e10f1b16543","tid":2316523,"uid":328850,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:02:05.000Z","msg":"兩個都唔可信 唔撚公道既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a623f052bde28105e761c95233d43d9ace59e1e6","tid":2316523,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c087abb4c07822163e9980f0d597e10f1b16543","tid":2316523,"uid":328850,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:02:05.000Z","msg":"兩個都唔可信 唔撚公道既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 開左alert? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}